{"title":"狐狸戴花","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐狸戴花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐狸戴花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐狸虽戴花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏不住尾巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花戴的越多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出的丑越大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧债尚未偿还"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧债尚未偿还，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又要把新债担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，人类的大债主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，能逃过惩罚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，造一颗炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一笔血案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要历史瞎不了眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惩罚的门不会关！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你念的经，什么经？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，侵略的强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永也不想洗手？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟的强盗经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念来又念去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时候念个虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓一吓墙头草；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时候念个葫芦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假装把刀枪一收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管你念白念黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝经上没有善字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若不是卖国贼，（或者糊涂虫）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁同你去拜杀人佛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美梦在安眠药中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝有一个美梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想作黄金大圣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想他的华尔街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥遥直上天空；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想他的刀枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为万世英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个美的梦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美梦在安眠药中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我告他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有如意算盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有定心丸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有七巧图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有照妖镜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有新阴谋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有老主意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁链吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的铁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能穿到天上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不叫你侵略王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的铁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能化成人民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不叫你侵略王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的铁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能拴住我的心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不叫你侵略王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴才，读白皮书吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴才，读白皮书吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书上有的是棺材。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要是读毕了业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棺材就把你装起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装起来，做什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你周游大海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火山跳舞，不赖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火山跳舞，不赖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要跳舞的，请来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁到火山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿女不用带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁到火山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棺材不用带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁到火山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣裳不用带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳一个裸体舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂不是更痛快？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死在那火山下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不要人致哀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四九年八月某夜写。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}